## 3. Gate Bulk Add vocabulary

### Status

Done.

### File

`app/(protected)/books/[userBookId]/vocab/bulk/page.tsx`

### What changed

Bulk Add now checks:

* book relationship permission
* vocabulary-saving feature permission

### Required access

Uses:

`featureAccess.canSaveVocabulary`

### Why

Bulk Add writes to `user_book_words`, so it should require vocabulary-saving access.

### Result

Expected behavior:

* Free learner using own book: blocked
* Full/trial learner using own book: allowed
* Linked teacher: allowed
* Super teacher/admin: allowed
* Random user: blocked by existing book access checks

